commit.message:
Removed Dependency on user Variable in setup Function

Variable user is most likely not initialized before setup function.
Need to come up with better approach to position HUD.

Client Connection Code Simplified

io() connects to window.location by default
Use Socket.io-client Npm Package Instead of CDN

Change Client Networking So That Hostname Is Determined Automatically

Instead of hard-coding hostname,
use window.location.protocol + '//' + window.location.hostname
Game Loop Waits Until User Is Defined
